data.title: Fern Emmett
data.meta_description:
Fern Emmett was born on March 22, 1896, in Oakland, California, USA. She began her career as an actress in the 1930s and quickly became known for her talent and versatility in the entertainment industry. Over the course of her career, she appeared in over 200 films, showcasing her acting prowess and leaving an indelible mark on the industry.
